comments: Boucher (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Jones (NOP) and makes marginal contact to his body.
Valanciunas (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Boucher (TOR) and makes marginal contact to his body.
Jones (NOP) makes marginal contact with two hands to Siakam's (TOR) body that doesn't affect his legal guarding position.
Birch (TOR) makes marginal contact with Ingram's (NOP) body that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Valanciunas (NOP) makes marginal contact with Birch's (TOR) arm after the release that does not affect his shot near the rim.
Jones (NOP) engages with Boucher (TOR) during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Temple (NOP) reaches around VanVleet (TOR) and makes marginal contact to his body that doesn't affect his SBQR.
VanVleet (TOR) veers into Temple's (NOP) path, but the contact initiated during his shot attempt is marginal.
Ingram (NOP) reaches backwards and initiates contact with Boucher's (TOR) lower body, but does not impede him during the rebound.
Siakam (TOR) makes marginal contact to Valanciunas (NOP) during the rebound.
Graham (NOP) commits a take foul on Birch (TOR).
